---
source: crates/tk/tests/scenarios.rs
expression: "p.run(&format!(\"{command} --help\"))"
---
Accept a triage Ticket into ranked, selectable work

Usage: tk accept [OPTIONS] <ID>

Arguments:
  <ID>  Display ID or Alias of the Ticket to accept

Options:
  -p, --priority <PRIORITY>  Priority to assign while accepting (P0..P4); required for a triage Ticket
  -h, --help                 Print help
